19
00:01:17,365 --> 00:01:19,286
It can be called

20
00:01:19,406 --> 00:01:23,126
a move of fate.

21
00:01:26,525 --> 00:01:28,126
I-It's...

22
00:01:29,926 --> 00:01:31,365
