174
00:07:16,806 --> 00:07:17,405
Forget it.

175
00:07:17,765 --> 00:07:19,606
Then let's go together.

176
00:07:20,486 --> 00:07:21,486
Okay.

177
00:07:22,166 --> 00:07:23,166
Eat the food.

178
00:07:32,726 --> 00:07:34,405
