179
00:07:35,205 --> 00:07:36,525
What kind of great place is this?

180
00:07:37,285 --> 00:07:38,285
There are even bats.

181
00:07:50,686 --> 00:07:51,686
You...

182
00:07:52,166 --> 00:07:53,166
(What's going on?)

183
00:07:53,566 --> 00:07:55,765
(Why is Zhao Feiyang
with Yanran and Bai Zhi?)

184
00:07:56,166 --> 00:07:57,285
(And their relationship...)

185
00:07:57,686 --> 00:07:59,405
D-Don't overthink it.

186
00:07:59,965 --> 00:08:00,965
The thing...

187
00:08:01,126 --> 00:08:02,246
