206
00:08:39,885 --> 00:08:40,885
Don't talk to me.

207
00:08:41,565 --> 00:08:43,206
I feel disgusted just hearing you talk.

208
00:08:44,206 --> 00:08:45,206
You...

209
00:08:47,925 --> 00:08:48,925
