211
00:08:51,645 --> 00:08:52,726
Can't think of anything?

212
00:08:52,966 --> 00:08:54,285
You'd better hope not to meet me

213
00:08:54,285 --> 00:08:55,405
at the Martial Assembly.

214
00:08:55,405 --> 00:08:56,405
Otherwise,

215
00:08:57,006 --> 00:08:58,126
I will make you

216
00:08:59,712 --> 00:09:00,446
