220
00:09:03,885 --> 00:09:04,885
annul our engagement.

221
00:09:05,486 --> 00:09:06,645
You and I are incompatible.

222
00:09:06,805 --> 00:09:07,405
What?

223
00:09:07,525 --> 00:09:08,525
Annul our engagement.

